      The Glenn Beck Program - 12/16/13Monday, December 16, 2013 10:53 AM


Why has Glenn gone to 3 separate performances of the Nutcracker? 

 Why does Glenn feel Russians are effective teachers?

  Who are the 3 most influential leaders in the world? 

 All these questions and so much more are answered on today's show. 


 Also, the guys discuss the recent shooting at a Colorado high school 
           and how a gun on campus prevented the shooting from being worse.
